result.title: Europe's Most Famous Abandoned Mental Asylum: Manicomio di R - Urbex Lost Places Italy
result.description:
Urban Exploration: Manicomio di R - Best Abandoned Italian Asylum (English and German subtitles are available!) Episode #109

► Do you want to help us producing even better content? You can support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/bwturbex
► Get our merch here: https://teespring.com/stores/bwturbex

We were dreaming of this exploration for many years! And finally the day had come. In the center of a small town somewhere in the Northern part of Italy this abandoned asylum is located. "Manicomio di R" is a place every one of us was looking forward to explore. Because it’s probably the most iconic abandoned place of the whole country. And maybe it’s even the most fascinating abandoned asylum in the whole world! From the outside the historical building complex looks rather unimposing and pedestrians would never guess what’s hidden inside here. In this episode we want to find out if the structure is still as impressive as it was in the past. And to unveil its sinister story...
